 Nobody, regardless of chromosomal, hormonal,

1:15:54.880 --> 1:15:56.360
 or any other background,

1:15:56.360 --> 1:15:58.560
 wants to have their normal levels

1:15:58.560 --> 1:16:00.880
 of testosterone reduced acutely.

