 So it's been this escalating arms race

1:49:25.080 --> 1:49:26.980
 of melatonin concentration

1:49:26.980 --> 1:49:29.760
 and it really does not look meaningful

1:49:29.760 --> 1:49:32.980
 for sleep in any way.

