2:30:21.860 --> 2:30:24.700
 It's almost like a J shape tilted over a little bit

2:30:24.700 --> 2:30:26.260
 and reversed.

2:30:26.260 --> 2:30:27.760
 So there's this strange hook.

2:30:27.760 --> 2:30:29.520
 What's going on here?

2:30:29.520 --> 2:30:32.060
 Right now, sleep science has at least

2:30:32.060 --> 2:30:35.320
